表格记录的代码预览

drop table if exists jl;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: jl */
/*==============================================================*/
create table jl
(
jlid int not null auto_increment,
pmpid int,
uid int,
pid int,
jpsj date,
jpjg int,
primary key (jlid)
);

alter table jl add constraint FK_Relationship_4 foreign key (pmpid)
references pmp (pmpid) on delete restrict on update restrict;
